'''tatya''' is a [[Telerin]]<ref>[[Vinyar Tengwar 42]]</ref> and archaic [[Quenya]] word meaning "second".
==Etymology==
The word comes from cardinal number ''[[Tata (Elvish)|tata]]'' [[Sundocarme|Root]]s [[AT]]-[[TA]].

==Cognates==
*[[Quenya]] ''[[attea]]'' (a newer form)
==See also==
*[[Tatyar]]
